Mail-SpamFilter version 0.08
============================

Provides a convenient interface for several spam filters.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

Currently provides interfaces for the following filters:

   SpamAssassin
   CRM114
   dspam
   WPBL
   SpamProbe
   Bogofilter
   Spamhouse ZEN DNSBL


